222
00:12:34,282 --> 00:12:36,166
Have you talked
to Alfredo?

223
00:12:36,168 --> 00:12:39,869
I have no need of a sponsor to
keep me from turning to heroin.

224
00:12:39,871 --> 00:12:42,288
