309
00:16:02,106 --> 00:16:04,040
What if I could offer you

310
00:16:04,042 --> 00:16:06,292
another entirely
unique experience?

311
00:16:06,294 --> 00:16:07,910
Surely, that would be
worth pursuing.

312
00:16:07,912 --> 00:16:10,112
