a high bar to clear.

313
00:16:10,114 --> 00:16:11,998
I'm fully aware of that.

314
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:13,449
But if you're not concerned

315
00:16:13,451 --> 00:16:15,051
about keeping
your clothes clean,

316
00:16:15,053 --> 00:16:18,137
