this would fit the bill.

317
00:16:20,257 --> 00:16:22,291
I did not know
there were tunnels

318
00:16:22,293 --> 00:16:23,593
underneath Camden Market.

319
00:16:23,595 --> 00:16:24,977
Yeah.

320
00:16:24,979 --> 00:16:26,562
Well, they're closed
