334
00:16:59,096 --> 00:17:01,547
Here we are.

335
00:17:01,549 --> 00:17:04,050
Thank you.

336
00:17:05,519 --> 00:17:08,221
Uh, should you
really be doing that?

337
00:17:08,223 --> 00:17:09,522
It's fine.

338
00:17:09,524 --> 00:17:11,023
