real estate tycoon.

373
00:19:21,189 --> 00:19:23,472
Other than that, nothing.

374
00:19:23,474 --> 00:19:25,140
Hi, Captain.

375
00:19:25,142 --> 00:19:27,076
Your gamboge tip paid off.

376
00:19:27,078 --> 00:19:30,813
That pigment you found came
